arStrings.szText: “What are going to do with this corpse?”
I’ve been growin’ a sickness. Deep in the swamp. All completely controlled with my care! Not too much. Not too little. But the Tree perceives it a threat. (sad sigh) It must be purged.
"...perceived mistake of mine" said sarcastically. Insulted the Tree thinks him incapable.
To the south, three corpses were prepared with possible cures. I’ll tend our friend here. Bring me a sample from the healthiest corpse there.
